<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>About Us - <%= appData.appName %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet"  type="text/css" href="/main.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About <%= appData.appName %></h1>
        
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong><%= appData.appName %></strong>, your personal companion for a healthier lifestyle.
        </p>

        <p>
            Our goal is to provide a simple, effective way for you to track your workouts, 
            monitor your progress, and stay motivated on your fitness journey. 
            Whether you are running, swimming, or lifting weights, we are here to help 
            you keep score of your achievements.
        </p>

        <h3>Key Features:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Log your daily activities and calories burned.</li>
            <li>Search through your history to see how far you've come.</li>
            <li>Check the weather before you head out for a run.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><em>Created for the Dynamic Web Applications Coursework.</em></p>

        <p><a href="/">Return to Home</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>